de.smits_net.games.framework.image

Class ImagePack

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.smits_net.games.framework.image.ImageBase
      • de.smits_net.games.framework.image.ImagePack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.awt.image.BufferedImage>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TiledImage

    public class ImagePack
extends ImageBase
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.awt.image.BufferedImage>
    A pack (collection) of images. This class can be used if more than one image has to be transferred. It can also contain only one image. The class has one "current" image, which can be retrieved using the getImage() method. The user can cycle through the images with the cycle() method.
    Author:
    Thomas Smits
